you ca n't die is a 1941 american comedy film directed by edward l. cahn and written by robert creighton williams . the film stars william boyd , andy clyde , rand brooks , frances langford , edward everett horton , ann sothern , william gargan , william gargan , edward everett horton , ann sothern , william gargan , edward everett horton , ann sothern , edward everett horton , roy barcroft , william " bill " henry . the film 's sets were designed by the art director wilfred arnold . the film was released by warner bros. on may 1 , 1941 .